      "text": "<p>Trebalo bi mu dati polje lozinke sa atributom polja <code>input</code> i atribut polja <code>pattern</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.isNotEmpty(document.querySelector('input[type=\"password\"]')?.pattern);"
